title: Ebro In The Morning - The Quintessential New York Hip-Hop Anthem
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 12/6.

Ebro and the crew debate what song defines New York hip-hop (11), the Gurus give their advice (40) and we find out who played themselves (7) !
